<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, single folio side, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>Excerpt from a geographical or travel narrative describing locations in the Mediterranean, including Venice, Modena, Candia, and Rhodes.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Body>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>vnd die jnsel ist bi ccc mil</Line>
        <Line>wit vnd ist der venediger</Line>
        <Line>Itz von kurtun vntz gon</Line>
        <Line>modun sind ccl mil vnd</Line>
        <Line>ist och ein hùbsch stat vnd</Line>
        <Line>ein ertzbstum vnd ist och</Line>
        <Line>der venediger ze modun</Line>
        <Line>wachset der rumanier vnd</Line>
        <Line>lit och do bi ein heilig heasset</Line>
        <Line>leo bi ij milan</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Candia</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>Itz von modun bis gon candia</Line>
        <Line>sind ccc mil vnd candia</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Creta.</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>vnd ist ein gros jnsel vj mil</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Virium</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>maluaier do vnd wachset der</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Malua.</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>der venediger</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Rhodg.</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>Itz von candia vntz gon rodis</Line>
        <Line>sind ccc mil wer aber</Line>
      </Paragraph>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
